{"id": "58f911693e82d3aefe44b8fd116df762fe9576609c07e5912935eab0089ee722", "item_id": "cc08ae9257:7", "text": "For extra realism, a procedural fog setup is also included and the thickness and fog height can be easily controlled via the 2 promoted parameters located on the"}
