{"id": "779bc2e0dc6221de64618b8a67f49b22b7b50bfc25a598e4c617cce571291723", "item_id": "cc08ae9257:13", "text": "The scene is all setup for you to render out both the wide and close cameras ... we've even setup denoising!"}
